summary.description: Analysis of early liquidity patterns in successful tokens

insights: Initial liquidity in SOL is the strongest predictor (34.2% importance)
Tokens with >5 SOL initial liquidity have 89% success rate vs 23% for smaller amounts
Model achieves excellent performance with ROC-AUC of 0.891
Time to first pool creation shows moderate correlation with success

recommendations: Deploy model to production for automated quality scoring
Create real-time alerts for tokens with high initial liquidity
Investigate outliers - successful tokens with low initial liquidity
Consider ensemble approach combining liquidity and DEX diversity features
